{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and they take away our luggage and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that took, like, you had the examination-- bend over, you know, you get undressed, you bend over and cough so they can see what you can hide things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not that sophisticated to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have anything to hide anyway, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a little food left, you know, because one thing we did have the-- the guard told us when we were picked up, tell the farmer to give you some food for a couple of days, right?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got-- and something terrible happened on that train ride.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I opened my package.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a piece of bacon in there and it was moldy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this one guy says to me, you can't eat that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I says, what do you mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, if I cut them off?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, that's going to poison you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He says, throw it out the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Throw it out through that little window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I cursed this guy for two and a half-- for two years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, why did he make me do that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I threw it out the-- you know, that little barbed wire window you can look through, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the way we checked where we were going, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so in the late afternoon-- in the meantime, we had nothing to eat yet, right?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were assigned to a certain barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was no room in the barracks, so they put him on a loft.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no blankets, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw in the corner there, there was some straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I grabbed two, one to lay on and one to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
